+Report any inconsistency involving coverage counters.
+
 Wcoverage-mismatch
 Common Var(warn_coverage_mismatch) Init(1) Warning
 Warn in case profiles in -fprofile-use do not match
@@ -936,6 +940,10 @@ fconserve-stack
