+
+mexpand-asm
+Target Report Mask(EXPAND_ASM)
+Expand certain inline assembly into rtl patterns that the compiler can
+better optimize.
+
+mextend-opt
+Target Report Mask(EXTEND_OPT)
+Optimizations on zero/sign-extension operations.
+
+mhazard-opt=
+Target RejectNegative UInteger Joined Var(tilegx_hazard_opt) VarExists
+Optimzie the schedule of instructions around micro-architecture
+hazards by selectively inserting nops.  0 = off, 1 = branches and
+jumps only, and 2 = on.
+
+mbme
+Target Report RejectNegative
+Compile using the BME headers and libraries
+
+mnewlib
